General.Name: Keypath Education International Inc DRC
General.Description: Keypath Education International, Inc. designs, develops, and delivers career-relevant online education solutions in North America, the Asia-Pacific, and internationally. Its services include predictive analytics and market assessment; develop, design, and deliver online degrees and courses; program marketing and student recruitment; and engagement, retention, and student outcomes services, as well as course development and placement online program management (OPM) services. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Schaumburg, Illinois. Keypath Education International, Inc. is a subsidiary of AVI Mezz Co., LP.
